{"tid":1422567,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事後討論 文宣角度 塗鴉 > 放火","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T18:12:13.000Z","uid":28759,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80d892b23c7a4a7b9a31a517251a8cdc3c9526f0","tid":1422567,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">塗鴉好處</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n快手<br />\n可以寫字清楚表達訴求<br />\n羞辱感重（內有強姦犯/鄉黑合作）<br />\n唔會 TK<br />\n冇濃煙唔會搞到街坊<br />\n開遮塗完閃冇人影到<br />\n俾人搜到有罐墨都冇咩問題<br />\n運送物資都安全<br />\n刑毀刑期短<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">火系壞處</span></span><br />\n<br />\n易 TK （燒親/濃煙）<br />\n要 setup （紙皮/燃燒物）<br />\n觀感印象差<br />\n無助於表達訴求<br />\n和理非唔敢企太近<br />\n俾人影到憑耳形可以拉你<br />\n俾人搜到火樽冇得拗<br />\n運送火樽坐硬<br />\n縱火刑期長<br />\n<br />\n我特別列出嚟係因為，放火唔好睇係事實，我哋依家只係用目的去合理化成件事。一個人冇目的周圍放火係唔啱，一個人冇目的周圍塗鴉，只係有啲反叛。要成功，就要不斷擴大支持嘅基數。如果一個嚟香港旅遊嘅人，咩都唔知，打開電視就見到黑衫縱火，佢第一印象就唔好，會冇咁易入口。<strong>要成功，就要爭取未支持嘅人支持</strong>，我地要令世界上每一個正常人都企喺我地呢邊！<br />\n<br />\n塗鴉俾人感覺係羞辱黑警，放火俾人感覺係挑戰黑警。兩者嘅分別係，一個會令人恥與為伍，一個會對家氣燄更高（見到學生俾人打你會嬲到爆，見到學生俾人劃花張枱呢，就冇咁嬲）。藍絲見到塗鴉，最多話你兩句，藍絲見到你燒狗竇呢，就分分鐘仲㷫咗，變得更加團結。（情況就好似政府 DQ 議員大家冇乜反應，政府對住學生放催淚彈呢，我地就即刻出晒嚟咁）<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，呢個時候放火都唔會失民意，因為歸咗邊嘅人，仇警心態都好重，所謂核彈都唔割。但放火唔失分嘅同時，有冇加分呢？就好值得商榷。每一次警察濫暴，我地嘅民意就更堅定，對家都係。唔係話天真到要拉對家過嚟，但滅對家嘅意志都好重要，冇咩必要都唔好令對家愈嚟愈團結，情緒愈嚟愈高漲。既然放火出核彈政府都係唔理，警察都唔會跪低，諗諗下放火都唔係太必要。同埋放咗火，媒體（包括外媒）就一定會用放火個畫面，啲塗鴉就冇人報。<br />\n<br />\n可能你會想問咁幾時先放得火？我都唔知，但主動挑釁一定唔係好時機。解鎖咗招技都唔係一定要用，絕對唔可以為用而用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>核彈都唔割，純粹想討論下好處壞處。</strong>"},{"pid":"863cdda5a51869bf04e54e2bd13d503fd09ba94a","tid":1422567,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:16:16.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f023388266dfb12a503622071533b8eb32c90182","tid":1422567,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4badde0fd57463c7e07bb8dc23c75a76860d08b7","tid":1422567,"uid":41549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"同意 推"},{"pid":"fb2ccaf225d97e2349d3c9eafbf72549f829a329","tid":1422567,"uid":300572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86317e6462749d32c5ed6c453958ab376dc0ba99","tid":1422567,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca05a3e429cbcef6da119d9da4db6c1cbdf12f0c","tid":1422567,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"50d688c0456e7c4459ea24623c01396a17250291","tid":1422567,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7544d90f55018fc26bd89c9c1b109113be6d45","tid":1422567,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764c99ac35458587f4f51af98c92d9d457835f51","tid":1422567,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:12:13.000Z","msg":"真放火老老實實危險而且好小學雞<br />\n燒一兩塊紙皮又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}